    <Text>static resources like fxmls should go in src/main/resources</Text>
    <Text>tests should go in src/test/java</Text>
    <Text>java should go in src/main/java, and should</Text >
    <Text>be in a package of its own (except main, obviously)</Text>

    <Label fx:id="welcomeText"/>
    <Button text="Hello!" onAction="#onHelloButtonClick"/>
</VBox>
